    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world devastated by a zombie apocalypse, humanity's last hope rests in your hands. <strong>Zombie Survivors: Eternal Nightfall</strong> is an intense roguelike survival game where you must face endless hordes of zombies and collect powerful upgrades to survive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strengthen your weapons with a wide variety of power-ups<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244140/extras/75a882ab9063925dd675a560989d4839.poster.avif?t=1730750808\" width=600 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244140/extras/75a882ab9063925dd675a560989d4839.webm?t=1730750808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244140/extras/75a882ab9063925dd675a560989d4839.mp4?t=1730750808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerful Upgrades:</strong> Collect and combine a variety of upgrades to create <strong>devastating builds</strong> and increase your chances of survival.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Hordes:</strong> Survive massive <strong>onslaughts of zombies</strong> that grow stronger the longer you stay alive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick Matches</strong> (20 Minutes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Apocalyptic Atmosphere:</strong> Immerse yourself in a <strong>visually striking world</strong> filled with danger and chaos as you fight to survive the apocalypse.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thrilling Soundtrack:</strong> A <strong>pulse-pounding soundtrack</strong> heightens the tension and excitement as you fight for survival.</p></li></ul>",
